snippet.title: Batteryman Recharges The World -  Trailer
snippet.description:
Restore power to the world after accidentally absorbing it all whilst holding back phone addicts in need of a power source!

A game made for Ludum Dare available on https://xavier-indie-gamedev.itch.io/batteryman
